                    (w-exp-dpz-ids-c01)   to   w-exp-dpz-ids-des
                                              (w-exp-dpz-ids-num)     .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-exp-dpz-ids-num    <    w-exp-dpz-ids-max
                     go to loa-dpz-ids-200.
       loa-dpz-ids-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     loa-dpz-ids-999.
       loa-dpz-ids-999.
