      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Uscita                      *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           go to     att-orf-ndo-999.
       att-orf-ndo-600.
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Se risposta negativa            *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
