      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-ofr-000      thru wrt-rec-ofr-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Write record [ofx]                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-ofx-000      thru wrt-rec-ofx-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo successiva *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-300.
       scr-mov-fil-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se modifica                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga nuova : come inserimento        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-rig (2)    =    spaces
