           perform   rew-rec-ofr-000      thru rew-rec-ofr-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rewrite [ofx]                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   rew-rec-ofx-000      thru rew-rec-ofx-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo suc-   *
