      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-oft-scl-ann       not  = w-slc-num-oft-saa or
                     rf-oft-cod-dpz       not  = w-slc-num-oft-dpz or
                     rf-oft-sgl-num       not  = w-slc-num-oft-sgl or
                     rf-oft-num-doc       not  = w-slc-num-oft-nds
                     go to slc-num-oft-500.
       slc-num-oft-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
