      *                                  * Editing                     *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      06                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-vis-not-rgd-prg    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * String                      *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           string    " "
                                delimited by   size
